# Mermaid Diagrams

## Node IDs and Labels
- No spaces in node IDs: use `camelCase`, `PascalCase`, or `_underscores`
- Special chars in labels: wrap in quotes `A["Process (main)"]`
- Avoid reserved IDs: `end`, `subgraph`, `graph`, `flowchart`

## Subgraphs
- Syntax: `subgraph id [Label]` (use explicit ID, no spaces)

## Edge Labels
- Special chars: wrap in quotes `A -->|"O(1) lookup"| B`

## Prohibited
- No HTML in labels; use notes or separate nodes
- No explicit colors or `click` syntax

## Diagram Types
flowchart, sequenceDiagram, classDiagram, stateDiagram, etc.
